  "body": "If you set up Remixd + Hardhat, it only works properly if a file is found in your shared folder called `hardhat.config.js`. In many of the hardhat projects, the config is using TypeScript, which will be `hardhat.config.ts`. \r\n\r\nTo reproduce, simply have the `.ts` verison isntead, and when doing `remixd -s ./ -u https://remix.ethereum.org` you will not see `hardhat is listening on 127.0.0.1:65522` appear.",
